description: For those who seek something special - distinctive, unique, and out of the ordinary - Penthouse N at Pier 4 offers bold New York–inspired style in the heart of Boston’s Seaport. With sweeping views of striking urban architecture and the vibrant streetscape below, this 3-bedroom, 3.5 bath residence embodies dramatic design and sophisticated living. A private half bath for guests enhances its effortless entertaining appeal.  Ascend the grand staircase to your private rooftop terrace and take in the ever-changing harbor below—a lively panorama of sailboats, barges and yachts set against the city skyline. As evening falls, pink skies fade to moonlight shimmering across the water. Complete with a stainless-steel grilling station and inviting spaces to relax or entertain, this rooftop oasis defines inspired city living. Building amenities further elevate your experience... state-of-the-art Fitness Center, Lounge, Common Kitchen and Roof Deck — complimented by (2) convenient parking spaces.
